high_descs: Walk straight to the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the coffee maker.
Turn right towards the stove.
Place the knife in the white cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around, walk towards the lettuce on the counter, turn right, walk towards the microwave.
Place the cup in front of the microwave on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife on microwave table.

high_descs: Take a step to your right then walk to the coffee maker that's on your left and face it.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the stove.
Put the knife in the mug that's to the right of the stove.
Pick up the mug that has a knife in it.
Turn around and walk until you're even with the microwave on your right then turn right and walk to it.
Put the mug near the bottom left corner of the table the microwave is on.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the counter where the coffee machine is.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the oven.
Put the large metal knife in the mug that is on the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the mug with the knife in it off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave.
Open the fridge and put the mug with the knife in it on the counter in front and to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left and face the coffee machine.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around, bring the knife to the sink, turn left and bring the knife to the counter right of the stove.
Put the knife in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with knife on the counter.
Turn around, bring the mug with knife to the microwave on the black table on the right.
Put the mug with knife on the black table next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with knife on the black table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and left to find the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the coffee mug.
Pick up the coffee mug and the knife from the counter.
Turn around, and then go to the right to find the microwave.
Put the coffee mug and knife down on the microwave cart.
anns.task_desc: Take a mug with a knife to the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to face the counter just left of the coffee maker
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn right and walk to the counter just right of the oven
Put the knife into the white mug on the counter
Pick up the mug from the counter
Turn around and walk across the room to the counter right of the fridge
Put the mug down on the front left edge of the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife on the counter
